 <robby@eecs.northwestern.edu> wrote:
 > Oh, I see. Probably only the first pause is necessary, then?
 
 There's an implicit pause in that you can't simultaneously press both.
  You have to hit the keys sequentially.  That's what I meant by the
 pauses.
 
 [Distinct from your keybindings issue, just answering your question.]
 
 Shriram
